Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A request?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for you, Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your destination is Kazalli.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazalli?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the client?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a woman in her 40s named\NSarah Florent. Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To commemorate Iris'\Nvery first commission,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,let's all get lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one in my village\Nwho became a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she heard about me\Nfrom someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just happy to be able to go home\Nand show off this uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all my friends and family\Nare going to want to come see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful not to get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that you are representing\Nthe CH Postal Company--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that was a disingenuous answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What did you just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received so many\Nvoting letter requests lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose it is the first election\Nsince the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With the House of Lords making moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the House of Commons\Ncandidates are desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the two of them will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the worst luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been a great opportunity\Nto show off my impeccable typing skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be typing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazalli is a village half-way\Nup the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,whose main industries\Nare dairy and agriculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no other particular\Ncharacteristics or history to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry we don't have much going for us.\N-There is nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When there is something of value,\Nit attracts crime and trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Northern Leidenschaftlich\Nhad iron and copper ore deposits,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which enticed the Gardarik Empire\Nto attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what caused the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle said he would volunteer to fight,\Nbut my aunt was against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he ended up not enlisting.\NWhich kept him safe, thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that apology for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you ended up injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you responsible for my injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be responsible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,An apology is admitting responsibility\Nand asking for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Times like this and when I first met her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never fully understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,who Violet Evergarden was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,LEIDENSCHAFTLICH\NKAZALLI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much more humid than Leiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hot in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a problem. I am accustomed\Nto these temperatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad! Uncle and Auntie, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? I just tripped...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Been so busy working that I strained it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-I get a lot of requests, you know.\N-That is also not accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ow! Oh, no. It's starting to hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be hard work\Nbeing a star Auto Memory Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dad! Stop exaggerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are you going to do\Nabout this letter then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will travel anywhere\Nto meet your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an Auto Memory Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's an Auto Memory Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The city Dolls are something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!\NI'm wearing my Doll uniform, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks good on you, Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a fine career woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean? Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,\Ndo you know a Sarah Florent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who requested me.\NShe should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the name of your\Nlate great-grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who requested you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could see you\Nif we hired you for a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you kidding me?\N-So, this was a false commission?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As it was written in our contract,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we do not accept the use of aliases\Nor false commissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W... Wait, Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now start your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter the correct name\Nin the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of invitation would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,An invitation to Iris' birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday is the day\Nafter tomorrow, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to invite a huge crowd\Nfor a big celebration this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have to write one immediately\Nif it's in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's so pretty!\N-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the invitation list?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many males on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, you are at that age.\N-So?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's time\Nyou get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's that supposed to mean?\N-You're our only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to come back and get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit your Doll job\Nand move back in with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you brought me back here?\NBy lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied to us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The most popular Doll in Leiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we're throwing you\Nthis birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, please type this guest list.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eamonn Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't send one to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though his name is on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why?\N-Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents are the ones\Nwho chose these guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you have the right\Nto remove him from the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-I'm the one who was requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just my stand-in. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished delivering my share.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just finished as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come over and have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, there isn't much\Nwe can offer you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not require much\Nin regards to hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I do not have much evidence\Nto base it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This view seems like a great example\Nof wonderful hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here you go.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your arm okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-I heard you became a Doll in Leiden.\N-Really? That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Montgomery just got\Nhis teaching certification exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hans is training to become a cobbler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Eamonn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris, happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I received an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You sent him one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After I went to confirm with your mother,\NI was instructed to send him one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because\Nyou sent him an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the connection between that\Nand suddenly feeling ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you not to send it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why did you do that?\N-I simply accomplished my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot understand\Nif you do not explain your reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He rejected me before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean\Nthat you approached him romantically,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but you were rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You expressed your affection,\Nbut you were turned down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what that means!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Iris doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's crying? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find someone better for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still talking about that?\NThis is all because of that party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I never came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tell them what?\N-About Eamonn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, I did.\N-Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not think it was a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were all\Nvery concerned about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't understand\Nother people's feelings, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had come to understand\Nemotions better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But people have very complex\Nand sensitive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone can express\Nhow they truly feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They end up contradicting themselves\Nor lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which makes it very difficult for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand what's true and what's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop bowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you didn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I always know\Nhow other people feel either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eamonn is a childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always very kind to me.\NI loved him for the longest time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just assumed\Nhe had feelings for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered why he didn't confess to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I told him\Nbefore we graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him, "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I only think of you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stay here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I wasn't a good writer,\NI studied hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and went to Leiden to become a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One needs a lot of courage\Nto say the words "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if the feeling isn't mutual\Nand it makes you want to flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for the major then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who's the major?\N-My superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a Doll so I could understand\Nwhat the major meant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,by "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that I was finally able to learn\Na little bit about Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The major provided his love to her\Nwho only knew the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And she is doing everything she can\Nto figure out what that means,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ms. Auto Memory Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you write a letter for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What type of letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,An apology letter to the people\Nwho attended the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure it's a polite\Nand heartfelt letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shall I send it to Eamonn as well?\N-Wow, you don't let up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But, yeah, send one to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be interested\Nin telling them how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to tell them\Nthrough a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotions too difficult to express\Nwill come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Mom and Dad,\NI'm sorry for ruining the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will send an apology letter\Nto the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, thank you for commissioning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This was actually\Nthe first time I was requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Work can be hectic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's what I've chosen, so,\NI will continue to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for always making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,please continue to watch over me\Na little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first commemorative letter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,from the future number one\NDoll in Leiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to her parents, who she loves very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you have everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let us know\Nif there's anything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,she's the one who typed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I will hand you an invoice later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're going to charge me?\N-Letter writing is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then how about lunch for three days?\N-That will not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it a company discount!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-The train is leaving.\N-Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Happy birthday.\N-Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the letter successfully reveal\Nyour emotions to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell from seeing their reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a good letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter you wrote got through to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was a good letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I write... a good letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you talking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Those flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're irises.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was born\Nwhen these flowers were in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why my parents\Ngave me this name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be okay\Nif I gave you a name then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling you'll grow into the name\Nwhen you're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,become someone\Nthat matches with their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by\NZensho Yamamoto
